      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
