    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent through a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure internal longevity. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Suspension components retain factory geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the precise turn-in and communicative steering rack expected of the marque. The exterior and interior show honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, but the powertrain and drivetrain remain robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
