    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. This car has been my reliable daily driver and has been kept in solid condition throughout my ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish, though you may find a few minor stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show only light bolster wear and all electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, it is sound\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and I have stayed ahead of all scheduled maintenance, including a recent oil change and brake inspection. It drives straight and true, offering a comfortable yet responsive ride. This is a well-cared-for example ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any looming repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
